{"tid":516061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家既細路識既野多左，但好多都好冇禮貌","createTime":"2018-01-01T04:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T23:27:56.000Z","uid":158738,"like":482,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"377cd8cde213766625f265c7f0b2f9e9dc17bb40","tid":516061,"uid":158738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:24:55.000Z","msg":"我返個份工有時都要教d 細路仔打機，但好多時教完佢地，佢地都唔會講唔該，同埋佢地既父母喺隔離都唔會出聲，有時送d 贈品比佢地，佢地都唔會講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但無可否認既係而家d 𡃁仔英文好左，識既野多左，但好多既家教反而冇乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n間唔中先見到一兩個細路既父母會話：「快d 講唔該/多謝哥哥啦！」"},{"pid":"dd15219846e5c02ad6393a598030890a971b7d36","tid":516061,"uid":29070,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n間唔中先見到一兩個細路既父母會話：「快d 講唔該/多謝哥哥啦！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真，好多都已經唔識講唔該<br />\n仲有啲大人顧著玩手提電話<br />\n由鳩個細佬周圍走<br />\n騷擾到人都唔理<br />\n繼續玩電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fded7a01240aff18054547cec94ddf26da6cb2f3","tid":516061,"uid":158738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822e3f236bf08b8714d270914e8220ea52b4d57d","tid":516061,"uid":61282,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"老豆老母本身都無禮貌，d仔女更加無啦"},{"pid":"22e3cf70c4b1714cbbfe15a34a205425f9a10ae2","tid":516061,"uid":158738,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"琴日有個細路唔識玩，我諗住教佢，佢一手fing 開我話識，後尾佢又係咁問我野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ad2ff23bc8263870fac9fcb4e96bc409b0523e","tid":516061,"uid":29070,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"quote":{"pid":"22e3cf70c4b1714cbbfe15a34a205425f9a10ae2","tid":516061,"uid":158738,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T04: